Doc: The Commodity specification of whether payments occur relative e.g. to the Trade Date, or the end of the month, etc.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The Commodity specification of whether payments occur relative e.g. to the Trade Date, or the end of the month, etc.
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.CommodityPayRelativeToEnum {
    # Payments will occur relative to the first day of each calculation period.
    CalculationPeriodStartDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the last day of each calculation period.
    CalculationPeriodEndDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the last Pricing Date of each Calculation Period.
    LastPricingDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the reset date.
    ResetDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the valuation date.
    ValuationDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the Calculation Date.
    CalculationDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the end of the month date for Calculation Periods which do not end on the last day of the month.
    CalculationPeriodMonthEnd 
    # Payments will occur relative to the start of the month date for Calculation Periods which do not begin on the first day of the month.
    CalculationPeriodMonthStart 
    # Payments will occur relative to the Effective Date of the contract.
    EffectiveDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the end of the month date for the month in which Pricing Days occur.
    PricingPeriodMonthEnd 
    # Payments will occur relative to the Termination Date of a swap or the last Expiration Date of an option.
    TerminationOrExpirationDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to the Trade Date.
    TradeDate 
    # Payments will occur relative to end of each week relative to the pricing period.
    PricingPeriodEndOfWeek 
    # Payments will occur relative to the first pricing date of each calculation period.
    FirstPricingDate 

}

CalculationPeriodStartDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the first day of each calculation period.
CalculationPeriodStartDate.Name: CalculationPeriodStartDate

CalculationPeriodEndDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the last day of each calculation period.
CalculationPeriodEndDate.Name: CalculationPeriodEndDate

LastPricingDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the last Pricing Date of each Calculation Period.
LastPricingDate.Name: LastPricingDate

ResetDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the reset date.
ResetDate.Name: ResetDate

ValuationDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the valuation date.
ValuationDate.Name: ValuationDate

CalculationDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the Calculation Date.
CalculationDate.Name: CalculationDate

CalculationPeriodMonthEnd.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the end of the month date for Calculation Periods which do not end on the last day of the month.
CalculationPeriodMonthEnd.Name: CalculationPeriodMonthEnd

CalculationPeriodMonthStart.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the start of the month date for Calculation Periods which do not begin on the first day of the month.
CalculationPeriodMonthStart.Name: CalculationPeriodMonthStart

EffectiveDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the Effective Date of the contract.
EffectiveDate.Name: EffectiveDate

PricingPeriodMonthEnd.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the end of the month date for the month in which Pricing Days occur.
PricingPeriodMonthEnd.Name: PricingPeriodMonthEnd

TerminationOrExpirationDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the Termination Date of a swap or the last Expiration Date of an option.
TerminationOrExpirationDate.Name: TerminationOrExpirationDate

TradeDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the Trade Date.
TradeDate.Name: TradeDate

PricingPeriodEndOfWeek.Doc: Payments will occur relative to end of each week relative to the pricing period.
PricingPeriodEndOfWeek.Name: PricingPeriodEndOfWeek

FirstPricingDate.Doc: Payments will occur relative to the first pricing date of each calculation period.
FirstPricingDate.Name: FirstPricingDate
